rows.label: <64E70BD1>
rows.name:
노아 일행이 소속되어 있던 콜로니

rows.label: <7DDF2D40>
rows.name:

rows.label: <75A88B70>

rows.label: <47933EB9>

rows.label: <3EA3C4E5>

rows.label: <53E97301>

rows.label: <907732AB>

rows.label: <C68EF16D>
rows.name:
